Spell Expertise / Conversion				KEY:Spell Expertise ~ Conversion			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellExpertiseFeatChoice								DESC:You may convert any memorized spell of equal or higher level into the chosen spell.																																																																																																																																																																							MULT:YES	CHOOSE:SPELLS|ALL[KNOWN=YES]																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.140
