Spell Expertise / Free Cast				KEY:Spell Expertise ~ Free Cast			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellExpertiseFeatChoice								DESC:You may invoke it once per day without expending a spell slot or requiring any components worth less then one GP (three times maximum).																																																																																																																																																														MULT:YES	CHOOSE:SPELLS|ALL[KNOWN=YES]																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.140
