Spell Shorthand / Cryptoglypics			KEY:Spell Shorthand PE~ Cryptoglypics		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellShorthandFeatChoice								DESC:You can read dangerous magical inscriptions, including Glyphs, Symbols, and magical Tomes without triggering the magic they contain.																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.141
Spell Shorthand / Encryption				KEY:Spell Shorthand PE~ Encryption			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellShorthandFeatChoice								DESC:You may convert spell formulas into complex mystical diagrams. While they take up only one page in this format regardless of level, no one without this enhancement can understand them at all.																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.141
Spell Shorthand / Formal Notation			KEY:Spell Shorthand PE~ Formal Notation		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellShorthandFeatChoice								DESC:Other spellcasters can prepare spells from your books without a spellcraft check or having to already have the spell recorded in their own books. Sadly, thanks to the special inks and procedures required, spellbooks still cannot be printed en mass.																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.141
Spell Shorthand / Runemaster				KEY:Spell Shorthand PE~ Runemaster			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellShorthandFeatChoice								DESC:You may mystically inscribe spells on bizarre mediums. For example, you may embed them in pearls, paint them on shields, or tattoo them as strange glyphs on the skin.																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.141
Spell Shorthand / Scribe				KEY:Spell Shorthand PE~ Scribe			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellShorthandFeatChoice								DESC:You may copy two spells per day, rather than one.																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.141
Spell Shorthand / Hieratics				KEY:Spell Shorthand PE~ Hieratics			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellShorthandFeatChoice								DESC:You have an inherent ability to Read Magic and can prepare spells from other character's spell books without a spellcraft check.																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.141


